Package se.jguru.nazgul.test.messaging

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MessageBroker
    Wrapper specification for a MessageBroker instance, to be controlled for the purposes of automated tests.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractJmsTest
    Abstract superclass for JMS-related tests, wrapping a MessageBroker to which all calls are delegated.
    AbstractRequestResponseJmsTest
    Abstract implementation of an AbstractJmsTest which sports a simplified setup for service-side transacted MessageListeners.
    AbstractTransactionalMessageListener
    Abstract implementation of a MessageListener which simplifies OOC JMS testing.
